          It completes two revolutions in 2 minutes and 7 seconds.<fn>Source:
          <url href="http://www.cedarpoint.com/public/park/rides/tranquil/giant_wheel.cfm"><em>Cedar Point's webpage</em></url>.</fn>Assuming the riders are at the edge of the circle,
          how fast are they traveling in miles per hour?
        </p>
      </statement>
      <answer>
